+++
date = "2019-09-11"
title = "Dynamic locality, split ergativity and adposition agreement in Avar"
host = "2019 Annual Meeting of the Linguistics Association of Great Britain"
publishdate = "2019-10-24"

+++

*Abstract*: In this talk, I develop a configurational approach to case and agreement in the Avar biabsolutive constructions.

This is a peer-reviewed talk, for the 2019 Annual Meeting of the Linguistics Association of Great Britain at Queen Mary University of London. 

You can view the slides [here](/papers/lagb2019-slides.pdf)


